Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what started it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Inaho.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm given to understand that it's\Nyou whom I owe my life to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's because\Nwe're in a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many times\Ndoes this make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure. And I wouldn't\Nsay that I've saved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a war, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a kind person, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.76,0:00:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all this is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.81,0:00:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will remain friends\Nafter all this is over, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.03,0:00:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am Asseylum Vers Allusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Princess Royal,\Ngranddaughter of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rayregalia Vers Rayvers,\NEmperor of Vers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I address the people\Nof Father Vers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call for an immediate cessation of\Nhostilities in this meaningless war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am safe.\NAlive and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is not Terrans who made\Nan attempt on my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was a plot by the Orbital Knights, who have\Ntheir sights set on an invasion of Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Terrans are innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the fighting immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then make peace with Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I beg you, put a stop\Nto this tragedy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Tharsis!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I retrieved it\Nfrom Castle Cruhteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was unworthy of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Its Aldnoah drive\Nis powered down...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Which means that\NCount Cruhteo truly is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Asseylum's location\Nhas been pinpointed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,via laser transmission\Nto the Moon base.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Moon base is under the control\Nof those who feel as I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness' proclamation\Nwill reach no one's ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The final battle is about to take place\Nat the enemy's main stronghold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even with the full might of a Landing\NCastle, it will be no easy feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My debt to your father is paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You may join my forces\Nor you may flee to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mars Knight Landing Castle descending!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Projected touchdown point,\Nwithin a 20km radius of United Earth HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, they aren't the least\Nbit interested in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Abandon surface installations!\NAll personnel, evacuate underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to say, I didn't expect them\Nto make a direct move on this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the war was\Nsupposed to end!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An act of futility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.65,0:05:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Commencing attack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy missile impacts!\NThey're bunker busters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bedrock has been perforated! Warheads\Ndescending towards base complex!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sally forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sky carrier, launch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Missile impacts and shield\Npenetration in 18 locations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vibrations believed to be enemy\Nmechanized force now descending!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kataphrakt platoons, get all\Nyour units launched ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shire Platoon, in position!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Falabella Platoon, in position!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Vibration source still closing in.\N59 seconds to enemy contact.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All units, prepare to engage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here they come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilate them, my faithful servants!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's an enemy Kataphrakt assault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Intercept team attrition rate, 50%!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Search for Princess Asseylum\Nand terminate on sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady, it's dangerous here.\NI suggest we relocate at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've revealed that my assassination\Nwas a lie, so why are they still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,War truly was their objective all along.\NThe assassination was merely an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It never mattered one whit\Nif I was alive or dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is not true at all! You are\Nthe beloved princess of Vers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.46,0:07:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, then, is this place\Npresently under attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no one left who can put an\Nend to the Orbital Knights' folly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there nothing more\Nthat I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Munitions loading 70% complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Launching a frontal assault\Nagainst United Earth HQ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:08:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be hard to hold negotiations\Nif the government collapses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They have no intention\Nof negotiating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Invade a territory with overwhelming force\Nand lay claim to it as their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no one to denounce them\Nover it, and no international law.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is primitive, pure war that dates back\Nto before the industrial revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten through\Nto the princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, ma'am. I'm paging the leader\Nof her security detail, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All pilots, stand by in your Kats!\NBe ready to move out at a moment's notice!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Warrant Officer Kaizuka,\Nis the Deucalion leaving?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beats me. This might turn into\Na defensive action.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mustang Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nao, you've got a phone call.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mustang 22.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall help, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seylum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All Vers weaponry is powered\Nby Aldnoah drives.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Landing Castles are no exception.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:09:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If its Aldnoah drive is shut down,\Nthe Landing Castle will cease to function.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How would we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the person who activated the drive loses\Nhis life, it will automatically shut down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, just like how the Deucalion fell out of\Nthe sky when you went into cardiac arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Also, one of the Vers emperor's bloodline\Nwould be able to forcibly shut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words... you are saying\N that you can shut it down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Understood. I'll escort you\Nto the enemy Landing Castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold your horses, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why are you always\Npulling this crap?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What crap?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know what crap! The way you say insane\Nthings with a perfectly straight face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we know she is unable to negotiate\Npolitically, her presence is of no benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if she is of tactical use,\Nwe should make use of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose, they're just going\Nto kill her, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the logical decision.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Logic is all it has going for it! How many\Nlives do you think that would cost?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we do nothing,\Njust as many will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that makes it okay\Nto pull this crazy crap?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My point exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, Yuki. But I think we should bet on\Nthe method with the best odds of success.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's all it is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I agree with his assessment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:31.81,Block,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao, do\Nyour best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, Highness.\NI'll run it past the Captain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The princess of the Vers Empire\Nhas turned her people against her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This war is not the will of Vers. It is all\Na scheme by a bunch of traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The responsibility\Nis mine alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.84,0:11:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let us hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Message from the Lord! "Ship located\Nin underground enemy base.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her Highness may be aboard.\NAll troops, proceed there at once!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That one hasn't\Nbeen rearm-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aldnoah drive, output stable.\NReady to lift off at your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Asseylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Currently on level 4!\NWill arrive momentarily!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Port gun turret #1 hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy infantry, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Engage them, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What Kats do we have ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're all secured in their racks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Send them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Princess Asseylum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's the Deucalion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy infantry on starboard stabilizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spin the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pivot the ship in place and don't\Nlet any enemy troops aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deucalion, coming about!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!\NIt's the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open hatch!\NBring her aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Princess Asseylum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket launchers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Objective located! Currently attacking\Nin underground dry dock!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I repeat, objective located!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not scared, I'm not scared,\NI'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You alive?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.23,0:13:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep the pedal floored.\NI'll cover you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rayet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on, come on,\Ncome on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A little closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eddelrittuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go! Hurry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seal hatch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Eddelrittuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her Highness is aboard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deucalion, lift off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Control, please open the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Control. This is Deucalion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.91,0:14:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tubes 1 through 4,\Nprepare to fire missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Set target, main gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Launch tubes open.\NReady to fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The ship from the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Back it up.\NGo back to the dock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold them off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The mission is as follows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Deucalion will evade the\NLanding Castle's attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and temporarily climb\Ninto the stratosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will then carry out a Kataphrakt\Ncombat drop from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's insane! We won't be able\Nto hide while we're falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be eaten alive by AA fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why we will drop unmanned,\Ndecoy Kataphrakts first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.33,0:15:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The main assault force will fall\Nthrough the jumble of decoys
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.38,0:15:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and aim for the Landing Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Altitude of 20,000 meters achieved.\NTurning over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drop Scarecrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The decoys might not work! And we don't\Nknow what kind of firepower they have!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've gone blind into\Nevery engagement so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But still!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once down, the assault team will\Ndestroy the enemy's AA guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and when their counterattack weakens,\Nwe ask Princess Asseylum to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Marito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See to the assault team selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go in the first wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I probably have more experience fighting\NMartian weaponry than anyone on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Multiple radar returns overhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-air warfare.\NWill intercept.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Decoy Kataphrakts hit!\NReleasing chaff and flares!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Assault team, launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mustang Leader to all units. In addition\Nto poor laser comms due to the blizzard,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}their jamming will get\Nstronger near the castle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't count on instructions until\Nwe're down. Fight independently.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang 11, roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang 22, roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang 33, roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mustang 44, roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let them hit me, please don't let\Nthem hit me, please don't let them hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're that scared,\Nyou're more likely to get hit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bullets are attracted to cowardice!\NBe confident, and the bullets will run from{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mustang 33!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Use my orange color\Nto guide you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nao, that's too fast!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll drop using the decoys as a shield,\Nand right after the objective leaves the clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fall until the very last second\Nand then decelerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Objective sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy Kataphrakt approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:19:00.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mustang 22, drop zone secured.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mustang 22, I have eyes on you.\NApproaching.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything stupid, Nao!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The more I thinned out their AA guns,\Nthe easier it would be for the stragglers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, wait! Are you saying\Nyou did it to help me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't right.\NComms are too clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry this isn't first class, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't go to\Nany trouble over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Control to Princess 1.\NStand by in drop position.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger. Princess 1,\Nproceeding to drop position.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens, protect your\Nfellow passenger. At any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Princess 1, prepare for drop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess 1, ready for drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Princess 1, drop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Princess 1, dro-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be right...\NThere's nothing on radar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-air warfare!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Protect the Deucalion!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Deucalion...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They transplanted the Aldnoah\Nfrom the other machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but with Orlane dead,\Nthey could not activate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, it was Princess Asseylum\Nwho activated it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Accursed ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.01,0:20:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mustang 44!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damage report...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:21:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Starboard side, antigravity devices\N2 through 7 offline...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are losing altitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Funnel all our energy\Ninto propulsion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Set course for...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...enemy Landing Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll board the damn thing\Nwith this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Seylum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I haven't gotten the signal yet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Warrant Officer Kaizuka!\NThree o'clock!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.59,0:21:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's... the Deucalion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All units, scatter!
